b: \"he will cut down the tallest trees\" (See: [[en:ta:translate:active]])"}, {"ref": "the lofty will be brought low", "text": "This can be translated with an active verb: \"He will humble the proud people.\""}, {"ref": "the thickets of the forest", "text": "\"the dense shrubs in the forest\""}, {"ref": "Lebanon in his majesty will fall", "text": "\"the forests of Lebanon will no longer be so grand.\""}]}, {"date_modified": "20150827"}]
